To use this script, make sure you have the necessary dependencies installed, such as the socket module in Python. You may also need to configure your network settings to communicate with the drone.


Here's a step-by-step guide on how to use the script for the Lenovo WiFi drone:



Connect your computer to the same network as the drone.

Replace the drone_ip variable with the IP address of your Lenovo WiFi drone.

Replace the drone_port variable with the communication port of your Lenovo WiFi drone.

Run the script using Python.

The script will send commands to the drone to perform actions such as takeoff, landing, and movement.

Customize the commands according to your desired actions.


